abstract: Coalition headed by European Union arranges for three planes to drop off supplies like warm blankets and clothing to war-torn parts of eastern Ukraine, as part of $53 million aid program.
lead_paragraph: The European Union delivered three planeloads of aid to eastern Ukraine on Tuesday, including blankets, tents, heaters and warm clothing.

headline.main: Ukraine: E.U. Sends Aid to East
